Node "LikeRat"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "IģI like rats. Rats are cute. Sometimes I go play with them. IģI also like the religious stuff. ItÆs just that the priests are a little weird sometimes and the wasters, theyģthey seemed to like me. ThereÆs nothing wrong with wanting to feel loved is there?"
 NPCFemaleText "IģI like rats. Rats are cute. Sometimes I go play with them. IģI also like the religious stuff. ItÆs just that the priests are a little weird sometimes and the wasters, theyģthey seemed to like me. ThereÆs nothing wrong with wanting to feel loved is there?"
