Node "Secound"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "eek! [She cringes when she sees you] umģHello. Are you g..going to let me stay? I havenÆt touched the Dream Juice since youģumģsaw me last."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "IÆm still thinking about it." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_GOOD playertext "I havenÆt heard anymore complaints about you, so I guess IÆll let you stay. Keep up the good work." linkto "Thanks"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If you havenÆt done anything wrong, why are you stuttering so much?" linkto "fear"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "LetÆs make a deal. I canÆt always be here to chase off your friends, so I need to find a more permanent solution. Tell me where they are getting the Dream Juice from and youÆll have proven your loyalty to the temple and what it stands for." linkto "toRatout"  notes ""
              }
}
